---
title: Golden Parmesan Fish Schnitzels with Cherry Tomato Salad & Smokey Aioli
description: It’s that time of the week, schnitty night! We’ve been looking forward to showing off this one. A sharp cheesy crumb coats tender fish to transform it into the ultimate schnitzel. Add a dollop of smokey aioli for a flavourful finish.

